      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "6-10-26 Gavin Notes\n\nAdd controllers with any button, then click which
    scene you want to load into. If you want your monster to be a flying monster,
    click on the appropriate button.\n\nFeatures added that require QA\n- Player
    locomotion (flighted and non-flighted monsters)\n- Collisions for Block Party
    and Monsterberry Munch Mania\n- Player Spawning and Respawning \n- Stage Hazards
    (Cars, Fire, Brick Shark, Toy Shark)\n- battle camera\n- player launching\n\nKnown
    Bugs and issues\n- Player circles can be weird, they are a temporary visual\n-
    elevator transportation on Block Party looks weird\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
